description: Here at Capt'n Crabby we are 100% authentic in everything we do! Starting with the way we marinate our meats, the Greek way & the way we make our crabcakes, the Maryland way! We make everything from scratch with fresh local ingredients, the right way! Our goal is to make food that people will want to eat & talk about over & over again! So, stop by our truck & grab a bite, but beware you may become addicted! And to all of our loyal Crabsters, We thank you for your continued support! See you soon!
name: Capt'n Crabby
